libs.content: find_library(matlab_iomp5_lib names iomp5 hints ${matlab_root_dir}/sys/os/ path_suffixes glnxa64 maci64)

deps.context:
cpmaddpackage(
                    name fftw3
                    options 
                        "enable_avx2 on"
                        "build_tests off"
                        "build_shared_libs off"
                        "enable_threads off"
                        "enable_openmp ${finufft_use_openmp}"
                    url "http://www.fftw.org/fftw-${fftw_version}.tar.gz"
                    url_hash "md5=8ccbf6a5ea78a16dbc3e1306e234cc5c"
                    exclude_from_all yes
                    git_shallow yes
            )

cpmaddpackage(
                    name fftw3f
                    options 
                        "enable_avx2 on"
                        "build_tests off"
                        "build_shared_libs off"
                        "enable_float on"
                        "enable_threads off"
                        "enable_openmp ${finufft_use_openmp}"
                    url "http://www.fftw.org/fftw-${fftw_version}.tar.gz"
                    url_hash "md5=8ccbf6a5ea78a16dbc3e1306e234cc5c"
                    exclude_from_all yes
                    git_shallow yes
            )
